{
  "stem": "6052.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Before my father-- or when my father tried to escape, he-- this was one rescue station, a temple or rescue station at [INAUDIBLE] hospital because-- and I will come to it very soon.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But before that, I wanted to dwell on the year when Hitler came to power.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "This was in 1933, and I remember it very, very well.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I looked through the window, and they marched at nights with their lights-- [INAUDIBLE], they called it-- and marched.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we were quite impressed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I was rather impressed as a child.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I did not know what this all means, what it symbolizes, what's going to be in the future.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, for many years to come, I did not know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I just became aware when I lived in Israel, and-- or rather, when I lived in the country where escaped to, to which I will also speak, that my father was murdered in Dachau that I knew here is something very, very bad going on.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My child memory is very clear about it, very clear, because I am reminded time and again in movies and books, and myself, what I saw.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In 1935, the Nuremberg Laws came, and I already could understand what it means.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a matter of actions against Jews, the [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Russian ?] laws, and all the laws which were really not something normal in the entire world.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was something abnormal which happened in Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And what-- this was made law.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A law was something which was inconceivable to humanity, but conceivable to those, and they hang to the law, and they acted according to the law, and they executed according of the law.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they stole from Jews, their money.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
